data.description: Through no fault of its own, this Beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bath Manuel Builders home in Carlyss Place Subdivision is back on the market! Upon entry you will notice the gorgeous wood beams in the living room which opens right up to the kitchen. In the kitchen you will find granite countertops, a dedicated corner pantry, a large island, and a natural gas range. The master ensuite includes his & her closets, double vanities, walk in shower and soaking tub. All window treatments are custom and are included! Out of the back door you will find a spacious porch along with a wooden privacy fence, leaving enough room to enjoy the water view! The community also offers a private pond and lighted fountain to enjoy year-round. Flood zone X. All Measurements +/-.
